. . .in the United States.

1592
02:38:08,994 --> 02:38:11,827
lt doesn't have to be this way.

1593
02:38:12,714 --> 02:38:14,909
We don't have to kill each other.

1594
02:38:17,114 --> 02:38:18,672
"Law Three:

1595
