There are going to be new laws!

1604
02:38:48,914 --> 02:38:50,233
Law One:

1605
02:38:51,954 --> 02:38:53,353
No more killing.

1606
02:38:54,234 --> 02:38:56,225
There's going to be peace!

1607
02:39:13,394 --> 02:39:15,305
How about it, Ford Lincoln Mercury?

1608
02:39:21,394 --> 02:39:22,668
Be a leader, Ford.

1609
02:39:25,834 --> 02:39:27,233
Law Eight:

1610
02:39:31,994 --> 02:39:33,268
Live. . .

1611
02:39:33,514 --> 02:39:34,993
. . .and let live.

1612
02:40:56,034 --> 02:40:57,831
Your daddy wrote to tell you. . .

1613
02:40:58,074 --> 02:41:00,634
. . .he'll be here as soon as he can. . .

1614
02:41:00,874 --> 02:41:03,342
. . .and that he loves you very much.

1615
02:41:10,954 --> 02:41:12,353
Mail's slow.

1616
02:41:13,794 --> 02:41:15,705
l'm going to have to see about that.

1617
02:41:46,794 --> 02:41:48,227
Your daughter.

1618
02:41:50,354 --> 02:41:52,345
Her name is Hope.

1619
02:42:21,834 --> 02:42:23,984
My father saW hoW fragile We are...

1620
02:42:24,194 --> 02:42:27,550
. . .and how quickly we fell
into the hands of tyranny.

1621
02:42:28,434 --> 02:42:30,106
He saw that ordinary men. . .

1622
02:42:30,354 --> 02:42:33,505
. . .could reach deep within themselves
and find courage.

1623
02:42:33,834 --> 02:42:37,304
He saw that if we began to communicate
as a nation. . .

1624
02:42:37,554 --> 02:42:39,351
. . .we could become strong again. . .

1625
02:42:39,594 --> 02:42:40,788
. . .united.

1626
02:42:41,514 --> 02:42:43,744
But he never did see St. Rose.

1627
02:42:45,274 --> 02:42:46,593
He said. . .

1628
02:42:47,194 --> 02:42:49,105
. . .there was too much to be done.

1629
02:42:50,714 --> 02:42:52,113
He'd made a promise.

1630
02:42:52,674 --> 02:42:55,666
And in keeping it,
he traded one dream for another.

1631
02:42:56,234 --> 02:42:57,792
With no regrets.

1632
02:43:01,114 --> 02:43:03,469
And so, in honor of my father. . . .

1633
02:43:40,714 --> 02:43:42,272
That was me.

1634
02:50:24,514 --> 02:50:26,505
Subtitled by
GELULA & CO., lNC.

1635
02:50:57,448 --> 02:51:01,202
The United States doesn't exist!

1636
02:51:08,048 --> 02:51:11,438
l'm giving you a chance at a life
that means something.

1637
02:51:13,808 --> 02:51:16,038
Redemption is within your grasp.

1638
02:51:16,288 --> 02:51:17,687
You are required
to show yourself.

1639
02:51:17,928 --> 02:51:20,761
But l'm not with these people.
l'm just passing through.

1640
02:51:22,768 --> 02:51:25,965
l can see it in your eyes.
You are a dangerous man.

1641
02:51:26,848 --> 02:51:27,644
Kill him!

1642
02:51:30,408 --> 02:51:32,922
You just head back the way you came.
We don't give charity.

1643
02:51:33,168 --> 02:51:36,319
l'm a representative of the United
States Government authorized. . .

1644
02:51:36,568 --> 02:51:38,957
. . .by the Restored Congress
to reestablish communication route.

1645
02:51:39,208 --> 02:51:40,163
What's that mean
in English?

1646
02:51:40,408 --> 02:51:41,966
lt means
l'm your postman.

1647
02:51:43,408 --> 02:51:46,480
You are nothing but a drifter
who found a bag of mail.

1648
02:51:49,608 --> 02:51:51,200
l have a feeling about you.

1649
02:51:54,448 --> 02:51:57,008
l know you'll do what's right.

1650
02:51:57,568 --> 02:51:59,763
Who's responsible. . .

1651
02:52:00,368 --> 02:52:01,437
. . .for that?

1652
02:52:06,968 --> 02:52:09,323
A man came through with mail.

1653
02:52:09,568 --> 02:52:13,356
Said he was a postman. Said that the
government had been restored back east.

1654
02:52:13,608 --> 02:52:14,643
What government?

1655
02:52:14,888 --> 02:52:17,197
The United States Government!

1656
02:52:17,448 --> 02:52:19,359
How about you?
Do you have a letter?

1657
02:52:19,728 --> 02:52:21,525
l don't have anybody to write to.

1658
02:52:23,808 --> 02:52:27,198
l took the uniform off a skeleton
to stay warm.

1659
02:52:27,448 --> 02:52:30,042
There is no Restored United States.

1660
02:52:30,768 --> 02:52:34,761
You gave them back their memories.
You've given us what we've forgotten.

1661
02:52:35,008 --> 02:52:37,158
You have a gift, Oostman.

1662
02:52:37,408 --> 02:52:39,558
You give out hope like it's. . .

1663
02:52:39,808 --> 02:52:41,207
. . .candy in your pocket.

1664
02:52:43,688 --> 02:52:45,838
l want all mail carriers hunted down.

1665
02:52:46,088 --> 02:52:48,318
-You've got to stay out of sight!
-l'm a postman!

1666
02:52:48,648 --> 02:52:51,003
l want the Oostman found.

1667
02:52:51,488 --> 02:52:53,206
l want him dealt with.

1668
02:52:54,408 --> 02:52:56,524
How much mail
can a dead postman deliver?

1669
02:52:56,768 --> 02:52:58,167
We're not going to stop!

1670
02:52:58,408 --> 02:53:00,046
Somebody might have to die!

1671
02:53:01,448 --> 02:53:04,246
You can't keep doing this.
You're not saving anybody.

1672
02:53:05,368 --> 02:53:07,120
Did l ever tell you
how l got to be a postman?

1673
02:53:08,688 --> 02:53:11,043
l don't know if you'd laugh or cry.

1674
02:53:11,928 --> 02:53:13,646
Do you hear me, Oostman?!

1675
02:53:13,888 --> 02:53:15,958
l said, "Ride! "

1676
02:53:16,208 --> 02:53:19,006
You want a war?! l'll give you. . .

1677
02:53:19,248 --> 02:53:20,806
. . .a war!

1678
02:53:41,528 --> 02:53:43,325
There used to be a postman. . .

1679
02:53:43,648 --> 02:53:45,604
. . .for every street in America.

1680
02:53:46,808 --> 02:53:49,606
They wore uniforms and hats. . .

1681
02:53:49,848 --> 02:53:50,963
. . .just like this one.

1682
02:53:53,448 --> 02:53:54,563
Getting a letter. . .

1683
02:53:54,808 --> 02:53:58,039
. . .made you feel like you were
part of something bigger than yourself.

1684
02:54:00,248 --> 02:54:02,808
l don't think
we ever really understood. . .

1685
02:54:04,208 --> 02:54:07,678
. . .what they meant to us
until they were gone.

